        <heading>864.  Attorney subject to disciplinary action</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 864.  Attorney subject to disciplinary action
An attorney may be subjected to appropriate disciplinary action for a wilful violation of any provision of Article 863, or for the insertion of scandalous or indecent matter in a pleading.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
